#### 4.2 gRPC 스킬 (grpc-skill/SKILL.md)

**Proto 파일 구조**:
```protobuf
syntax = "proto3";
package chat;

option java_multiple_files = true;
option java_package = "com.maum.backend.protobuf.chat";

service ChatService {
  rpc SendMessage(SendMessageRequest) returns (SendMessageResponse);
  rpc GetMessages(GetMessagesRequest) returns (GetMessagesResponse);
  rpc SendImage(SendImageRequest) returns (SendImageResponse);
}

message ChatImage {
  string id = 1;
  string message_id = 2;
  string url = 3;
  string created_at = 4;
}
```

**gRPC Service 구현** (chat 모듈):
```kotlin
@GrpcService
class ChatGrpcService(
    private val chatService: ChatService,
) : ChatServiceGrpc.ChatServiceImplBase() {

    override fun sendImage(
        request: SendImageRequest,
        responseObserver: StreamObserver<SendImageResponse>,
    ) {
        try {
            val response = chatService.sendImage(request.userId, request)
            responseObserver.onNext(response)
            responseObserver.onCompleted()
        } catch (e: Exception) {
            responseObserver.onError(Status.INTERNAL.asException())
        }
    }
}
```

#### 4.3 GraphQL 스킬 (graphql-skill/SKILL.md)

**GraphQL Schema** (graphql/.../resources/graphql/chat.graphqls):
```graphql
type ChatImage {
    id: ID!
    messageId: ID!
    url: String!
    createdAt: String!
}

input SendImageInput {
    roomId: ID!
    imageUrl: String!
    caption: String
}

extend type Mutation {
    sendChatImage(input: SendImageInput!): ChatImage!
    sendChatMessage(roomId: ID!, content: String!): ChatMessage!
}

extend type Query {
    chatMessages(roomId: ID!, limit: Int, offset: Int): [ChatMessage!]!
}
```

**GraphQL Controller** (graphql/.../controller/chat/):
```kotlin
@Controller
class ChatController(
    private val chatService: ChatService,
) {
    @MutationMapping
    @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
    fun sendChatImage(
        @UserId userId: String,
        @Argument input: SendImageInput,
    ): ChatImage {
        val response = chatService.sendImage(userId, input.roomId, input.imageUrl)
        return response.toResponse()
    }
}
```

**GraphQL Service** (graphql/.../service/chat/):
```kotlin
@Service
class ChatService {
    @GrpcClient("chat-grpc")
    private lateinit var stub: ChatServiceGrpc.ChatServiceBlockingStub

    fun sendImage(userId: String, roomId: String, imageUrl: String): SendImageResponse {
        val request = SendImageRequest.newBuilder()
            .setUserId(userId)
            .setRoomId(roomId)
            .setImageUrl(imageUrl)
            .build()
        return try {
            stub.sendImage(request)
        } catch (e: StatusRuntimeException) {
            throw CustomGraphQLException(e.trailers!!, e.status.description)
        }
    }
}
```

